Readme File:
***********************************
Counter Strike:Source
***********************************
TITLE: gg_zoffice
AUTHOR: Zaennon_
E-MAIL: askurflint@hotmail.com

FILENAME: gg_zoffice.bsp
FILESIZE: 4,17 MB (4 382 720 byte)
DATE RELEASED: August 10, 2009



INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:

Place the gg_zoffice.bsp in 
"\Steam\steamapps\[username]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" folder,
run the game and create server!

DESCRIPTION:

An indoor gungame map based on cs_office theme.
14 spawns for each team.
This is my fourth map i made, 
I had some friends testplay it and there are no known bugs atm.
But, if you find any contact me via mail askurflint@hotmail.com so i can fix it.
Thanks in advance.

/Zaennon
